item.title: braces
item.description: 12:34 Friday 06 October 2017 JST Dang I am too old for this, but I just go googoo seeing this cute flight attendant with braces. Top and bottom teeth. I’m pretty sure I am projecting my crush on the character Sam from that old daytime drama The Facts of Life.
